docs {
  # Create Directory
  
  Create a new directory. Creates parent directories if needed.
  
  ## Request Body
  - `dirPath` (string, required): Absolute path for the new directory
  
  ## Response
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "path": "/path/to/new-directory"
  }
  ```
}
